        fieldset
          button.puputchik-filter__toggle(type="button")
            | Хобби
            span :
          .puputchik-filter__content
            ul.puputchik-filter__list
              li
                label
                  input.visually-hidden(type="checkbox", id="hobby-rock", checked)
                  span.puputchik-filter__checkbox
                    +check("check")
                  | Спортзал
              li
                label
                  input.visually-hidden(type="checkbox", id="hobby-rap")
                  span.puputchik-filter__checkbox
                    +check("check")
                  | Кальян
